<view class="trial-page">
  <view class="trial-hero card">
    <text class="trial-badge">限时体验</text>
    <text class="trial-title">免费刷题课体验</text>
    <text class="trial-desc">不再盲目刷题，先找卡点，再开药方。先体验一轮完整节奏，再决定是不是继续。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="trial-metrics">
    <view class="trial-metric card">
      <text class="trial-metric-value">8</text>
      <text class="trial-metric-label">核心卡点</text>
    </view>
    <view class="trial-metric card">
      <text class="trial-metric-value">4</text>
      <text class="trial-metric-label">场直播拆题</text>
    </view>
    <view class="trial-metric card">
      <text class="trial-metric-value">99</text>
      <text class="trial-metric-label">全勤可返</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="trial-section card card-pain">
    <text class="trial-pain-title">“你已经刷了很多题，分数却还在原地。”</text>
    <text class="trial-pain-desc">问题往往不在于不努力，而在于一直在用“对答案”代替“找失分点”。没有诊断的训练，只是在重复错误。</text>
    <view class="trial-pain-box">
      <text class="trial-pain-box-text">这套体验课的核心逻辑是：先诊断失分根源，再对症开方，然后用纠偏 + 刷题去验证改变。</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="trial-section card card-warm">
    <text class="trial-section-title">这不是普通刷题</text>
    <text class="trial-section-copy">很多人刷了很多题，分数却一直在原地。问题不在于不努力，而在于一直没有找到真正的失分点。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="trial-section card">
    <text class="trial-section-title">八大卡点体系</text>
    <view class="trial-point-block trial-point-block-red">
      <view class="trial-point-head">
        <text class="trial-point-badge trial-point-badge-red">红标卡点</text>
        <text class="trial-point-head-note">不解决很难真正起分</text>
      </view>
      <view class="trial-point-item">
        <text class="trial-point-name">游走式找点</text>
        <text class="trial-point-desc">解决“读了很多遍材料，还是抓不到真正要点”的底层问题。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="trial-point-item">
        <text class="trial-point-name">提炼转述错误</text>
        <text class="trial-point-desc">解决“看懂了却写不出来，或者总在照抄原文”的失分问题。</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="trial-point-block trial-point-block-yellow">
      <view class="trial-point-head">
        <text class="trial-point-badge trial-point-badge-yellow">黄标卡点</text>
        <text class="trial-point-head-note">解决之后提分会更快</text>
      </view>
      <view class="trial-point-grid">
        <text class="trial-point-grid-item">对策推导错误</text>
        <text class="trial-point-grid-item">分析结构错误</text>
        <text class="trial-point-grid-item">公文结构错误</text>
        <text class="trial-point-grid-item">作文立意错误</text>
        <text class="trial-point-grid-item">作文逻辑不清晰</text>
        <text class="trial-point-grid-item">作文表达不流畅</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="trial-point-block trial-point-block-blue">
      <view class="trial-point-head">
        <text class="trial-point-badge trial-point-badge-blue">蓝标卡点</text>
        <text class="trial-point-head-note">后期冲刺时最适合发力</text>
      </view>
      <text class="trial-point-summary">对应目标考试的特殊考法和拔高要求，属于后置位优化，但对冲刺高分很关键。</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="trial-section card">
    <text class="trial-section-title">你会体验到什么</text>
    <view class="trial-step">
      <text class="trial-step-index">01</text>
      <view class="trial-step-copy">
        <text class="trial-step-title">先识别失分卡点</text>
        <text class="trial-step-desc">不是对答案，而是先判断你到底卡在找点、结构，还是作文表达。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="trial-step">
      <text class="trial-step-index">02</text>
      <view class="trial-step-copy">
        <text class="trial-step-title">直播剖作业 + 追问式反馈</text>
        <text class="trial-step-desc">每一轮刷题都会拆到“为什么错”，不是只给标准答案。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="trial-step">
      <text class="trial-step-index">03</text>
      <view class="trial-step-copy">
        <text class="trial-step-title">形成完整提分闭环</text>
        <text class="trial-step-desc">共识、学习、纠偏、刷题、测验、验证，体验一套真正能提分的节奏。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="trial-section card">
    <text class="trial-section-title">适合谁先来体验</text>
    <view class="trial-tag-row">
      <text class="trial-tag">申论分数一直卡住</text>
      <text class="trial-tag">不确定问题在哪</text>
      <text class="trial-tag">想先试试再决定</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="trial-section card">
    <text class="trial-section-title">真实提分案例</text>
    <view class="trial-case-grid">
      <view class="trial-case-card">
        <text class="trial-case-badge">在职学员</text>
        <text class="trial-case-score">57.5 → 78</text>
        <text class="trial-case-copy">长周期备考里，先补红标底层卡点，再做黄标题型突破，最后完成考前冲刺。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="trial-case-card">
        <text class="trial-case-badge">精准诊断</text>
        <text class="trial-case-score">63.5 → 75.5</text>
        <text class="trial-case-copy">先识别“游走式找点”和“作文立意错误”，再围绕这两个点完成完整纠偏闭环。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="trial-section card">
    <text class="trial-section-title">这套体验课的三个核心点</text>
    <view class="trial-core-grid">
      <view class="trial-core-card">
        <image class="trial-core-icon" src="{{uiIcons.spark}}" mode="aspectFit" />
        <text class="trial-core-title">追问式自评</text>
        <text class="trial-core-desc">一层层追问你的真实思路，把错误暴露出来，而不是只看结果对错。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="trial-core-card">
        <image class="trial-core-icon" src="{{uiIcons.video}}" mode="aspectFit" />
        <text class="trial-core-title">直播剖作业</text>
        <text class="trial-core-desc">不是泛泛讲题，而是当场拆“为什么会错”，逼出真正的卡点。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="trial-core-card trial-core-card-highlight">
        <image class="trial-core-icon" src="{{uiIcons.check}}" mode="aspectFit" />
        <text class="trial-core-title">全勤可返</text>
        <text class="trial-core-desc">4 场体验完整跟下来，押金可返，相当于用行动换一套提分方法论。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="trial-footer card card-dark">
    <text class="trial-footer-title">先体验，再判断</text>
    <text class="trial-footer-desc">你不需要先相信全部，只需要先体验一轮，看看这套方法是不是适合你。</text>
    <view class="trial-btn" bindtap="goStartTrial">
      <text class="trial-btn-text">进入体验课</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
